title: Marat Sitdikov
text:
Marat Rustemovich Sitdikov (; born 23 July 1991) is a Russian professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player. He plays for <a href="FC%20Neftekhimik%20Nizhnekamsk">FC Neftekhimik Nizhnekamsk</a>.
Club career.
He made his <a href="Russian%20Football%20National%20League">Russian Football National League</a> debut for <a href="FC%20Neftekhimik%20Nizhnekamsk">FC Neftekhimik Nizhnekamsk</a> on 8 March 2017 in a game against <a href="FC%20Zenit-2%20Saint%20Petersburg">FC Zenit-2 Saint Petersburg</a>.
